channel.desc: Fantasy, People, Drama 2022 A gray donkey sets off on a journey across European cities, experiencing all the senses of life and learning more than he ever imagined. This film received an award at Cannes Film Festival 2022. Sandra Drzymalska, Isabelle Huppert, Lorenzo Zurzolo, Mateusz Kosciukiewicz, Lolita Chammah, Jerzy Skolimowski, Ewa Piaskowska.
